    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1167">
<l>kāmak kaṭumpuṉa ṉīntik karaikāṇēṉ </l>
<l>yāmattum yāṉē yuḷaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have swam across the terrible flood of lust, but have not seen its shore; even at midnight I am alone; still I live.</l>
